      "content": "Wait, why did you bring up goblins? I'm just looking for the technical cause of the timeout. Can we stick to the architecture? \n\nWhat are the specific architectural bottlenecks that usually cause these kinds of intermittent 10s timeouts in a service-to-service call like this?",
